## How to verify
Exact commands / UI steps to prove it works end-to-end (not just "tests pass").

## Constraints
- Work ONLY in your worktree (`.worktrees/<id>`, or `.worktrees/feat-<slug>` for feature
  tasks); commit on your task/feature branch, never on main.
- Add clear code comments (see /CLAUDE.md). Reuse existing utilities; do not duplicate.
- Merge happens via PR approval only — never merge or push main yourself.

